Class PairObjDouble

  • java.lang.Object
    • utils.PairObjDouble
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PairObjTwoDouble

    public class PairObjDouble
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable
    utility class with the same semantics as PairIntDouble except the first (key) object in a PairObjDouble can be any Object. Notes:
    • 20191227: modified hashCode() to work according to Bloch's suggestions.
